        <name>AI Council Assessment</name>
        <styleUrl>#intel</styleUrl>
        <description>The provided information offers a detailed overview of various aspects of U.S. military operations, procurement strategies, strategic nuclear capabilities, special operations activities, and specific operational deployments. It highlights ongoing efforts in defense budgets, international relations, maritime interdiction, carrier strike groups, drone strikes, special forces training, and the potential use of advanced surveillance technology by Iran. The data also includes recent developments such as U.S. military draft registration plans and the testing of specialized aircraft for naval operations.</description>
